@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About US";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
    <title>About Us - Bracelatte Company</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Light blue background */
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White background for content */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow for content box */
            border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners for the content box */
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333; /* Dark Gray */
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #555555; /* Medium Gray */
        }
        p {
            color: #666666; /* Light Gray */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>


<h2>Welcome to Deeor!</h2>
<p>
    At Bracelatte, we believe in the power of accessories to transform not just your look, but your entire day. Founded with a passion for style and a love for craftsmanship, we specialize in creating unique, high-quality bracelets that blend fashion with functionality.
</p>

<h2>Our Story</h2>
<p>
    Bracelatte was born from the simple idea that accessories should be more than just adornments. Our founders, driven by a love for design and a deep appreciation for artisanal craftsmanship, set out to create a brand that offers more than just beautiful bracelets. They envisioned pieces that tell a story, pieces that connect with the wearer on a personal level, and pieces that stand the test of time.
</p>

<h2>Our Products</h2>
<p>
    Every Bracelatte bracelet is a testament to our commitment to quality and innovation. We meticulously select the finest materials and combine them with intricate designs to create bracelets that are not only stunning but also durable. Our collection features a wide range of styles, from elegant and minimalist to bold and statement-making, ensuring that there is something for everyone.
</p>

<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<p>
    Our mission at Bracelatte is to inspire confidence and self-expression through our beautifully crafted accessories. We aim to create pieces that are as unique as the individuals who wear them, encouraging our customers to embrace their own style and make a statement wherever they go.
</p>

<h2>Sustainability</h2>
<p>
    We are committed to sustainability and ethical practices. We believe in creating products that are not only beautiful but also responsibly made. From sourcing eco-friendly materials to ensuring fair labor practices, we strive to make a positive impact on the world through our business practices.
</p>

<h2>Join Our Community</h2>
<p>
    Bracelatte is more than just a brand; it's a community of like-minded individuals who appreciate the finer things in life. Follow us on our journey as we continue to explore new designs, materials, and inspirations. Join us on social media to stay updated with our latest collections, behind-the-scenes looks, and exclusive offers.
</p>

<h2>Thank You</h2>
<p>
    Thank you for choosing Bracelatte. We are honored to be a part of your style journey and look forward to helping you shine with our exquisite bracelets.
</p>
</body>
</html>